----------|----------
Epic | #1111 Search
T-shirt size: SML | 
User Story | As a UX developer , I should be able to call a search API for roles packs and users with a request, and I get back a valid response .
Description | Search API parse request, build response. Build the internal search structure and search manager indirection layer.
Acceptance criteria | able to issue a search request and get back a valid search response (not a correct search response)

Query from UI (view in edit mode to see correct indenting):

GET /api/search
Search request format:
{
  "query": {
    "search_input": string to be searched,
    "search_object_types": [
      "role",
      "pack"
    ],
    "page_size": "20",
    "page": "2"
  }
}


Search response format:
{  
  "data": {  
    "roles": [  
      {
        "name": ""
      }
    ],
    "packs": [  
      {
        "name": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  "page": 1,
  "total_pages": 99 
}
